#. Id: 18052-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 0.0
#. -- Parent line: -
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#. -- Condition: My Race(s): Hive Prince
#: 18052-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "... I won't be broken... I won't be broken..."
msgstr "......我不會被打破......我不會被打破......"

#. Id: 18057-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 1.0
#. -- Parent line: 0 (18052-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 18057-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Hey, you okay in there?"
msgstr "嘿，你還好嗎？"

#. Id: 18058-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 2.0
#. -- Parent line: 1 (18057-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 18058-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Nobody owns me... I promised myself... after I left the queen, left the Hive... I promised I would never... NEVER serve a master again. They won't break me... they won't..."
msgstr "沒有人擁有我......我答應了自己......在我離開女王后，離開了蜂巢......我保證我永遠不會......再也不會為主人服務了。他們不會打破我......他們不會......"

#. Id: 18058-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 2.1
#. -- Parent line: 1 (18057-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 18058-Dialogue.mod:1
msgid "... They can enslave my body, but... they can't enslave my mind... Not again. I already left one master, I'll never serve another..."
msgstr "......他們可以奴役我的身體，但......他們不能奴役我的思緒......不再是。我已經離開了一位大師，我永遠不會再為另一位大師服務......"

#. Id: 18064-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 3.0
#. -- Parent line: 2 (18058-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 18064-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Be strong. You can survive this, we can be free again"
msgstr "要堅強。你可以活下來，我們可以再次自由"

#. Id: 18064-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 3.1
#. -- Parent line: 2 (18058-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 18064-Dialogue.mod:1
msgid "You broke free from the Hive, right? You can break free from here too."
msgstr "你掙脫了蜂巢，對嗎？你也可以從這裡擺脫。"

#. Id: 18076-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 4.0
#. -- Parent line: 3 (18064-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 18076-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Free again... Okay, so let's do something. You and me, bust out together."
msgstr "再次自由......好的，讓我們做點什麼吧。你和我，一起出去玩。"

#. Id: 18076-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 4.1
#. -- Parent line: 3 (18064-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 18076-Dialogue.mod:1
msgid "Yeah, you're right. We'll survive... But let's do something about it, I say we break out together..."
msgstr "是啊，你說得對。我們會活下來......但是我們要做點什麼，我說我們一起爆發......"

#. Id: 18077-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 5.0
#. -- Parent line: 4 (18076-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 18077-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Okay, I'll handle the locks, leave it to me"
msgstr "好的，我會處理鎖，留給我"

#. Id: 18078-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 5.0
#. -- Parent line: 4 (18076-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 18078-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Wait... I don't want to anger the masters..."
msgstr "等等......我不想激怒大師......"

#. Id: 19850-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 6.0
#. -- Parent line: 5 (18078-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 19850-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Kch. Freedom is won. Not given..."
msgstr "KCH。自由贏了。沒有給..."

#. Id: 19851-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 7.0
#. -- Parent line: 6 (19850-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 19851-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Don't let them break you!"
msgstr "不要讓他們打破你！"

#. Id: 18079-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 5.0
#. -- Parent line: 4 (18076-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 18079-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "That's the spirit. Let's do this"
msgstr "就是那種精神。我們開工吧"

#. Id: 18099-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 5.0
#. -- Parent line: 4 (18076-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 18099-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "With you? Sorry, I'll have a better chance on my own..."
msgstr "和你？對不起，我自己有更好的機會......"

#. Id: 19852-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 6.0
#. -- Parent line: 5 (18099-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 19852-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "What?! No, don't leave me here!"
msgstr "什麼？！不，不要把我留在這裡！"

#. Id: 19853-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 7.0
#. -- Parent line: 6 (19852-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 19853-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "I can help you..."
msgstr "我能幫你..."

#. Id: 18082-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 4.0
#. -- Parent line: 3 (18067-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 18082-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Just trying to keep my mind my own. I worked hard for my freedom from the Hive... and now THIS happens? I can't catch a break..."
msgstr "只是想讓我的思緒成為我自己的想法。我為Hive的自由而努力工作......現在發生這種情況了嗎？我不能休息一下......"

#. Id: 18083-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 5.0
#. -- Parent line: 4 (18082-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 18083-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "I can't either, pal, trust me"
msgstr "我也不能，朋友，相信我"

#. Id: 18084-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 5.0
#. -- Parent line: 4 (18082-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 18084-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Then let's break out. Either we find freedom or we find death"
msgstr "然後讓我們爆發吧。我們要么找到自由，要么找到死亡"

#. Id: 18085-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 6.0
#. -- Parent line: 5 (18084-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 18085-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "... A fair gamble I suppose. Okay, what's the plan?"
msgstr "......我想是一場公平的賭博。好的，計劃是什麼？"

#. Id: 18086-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 5.0
#. -- Parent line: 4 (18082-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 18086-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Whatever... (Turn from them)"
msgstr "無論如何......（轉身）"

#. Id: 18066-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 3.0
#. -- Parent line: 2 (18058-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 18066-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Well, from where I'm standing it looks like you're pretty broken..."
msgstr "好吧，從我站立的地方來看，你看起來很糟糕......"

#. Id: 18081-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 4.0
#. -- Parent line: 3 (18066-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 18081-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Well you're wrong... I won't be broken..."
msgstr "那你錯了......我不會被打破......"

#. Id: 19855-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 5.0
#. -- Parent line: 4 (18081-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 19855-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "And last thing I need is your pessimism, stranger."
msgstr "我最不需要的是你的悲觀主義，陌生人。"

#. Id: 18063-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 3.0
#. -- Parent line: 2 (18058-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 18063-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "So let's do something about it. Let's get out of here"
msgstr "讓我們來做點什麼吧。我們離開這裡吧"

#. Id: 18071-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 4.0
#. -- Parent line: 3 (18063-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 18071-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "... I'll do whatever it takes to be free again. What's the plan?"
msgstr "......我會盡一切可能再獲得自由。計劃是什麼？"

#. Id: 18072-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 5.0
#. -- Parent line: 4 (18071-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 18072-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "I'll handle the locks, leave it to me"
msgstr "我會處理鎖，留給我"

#. Id: 18090-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 6.0
#. -- Parent line: 5 (18072-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 18090-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Okay. Let's do it"
msgstr "好的。我們開始做吧"

#. Id: 18090-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 6.1
#. -- Parent line: 5 (18072-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 18090-Dialogue.mod:1
msgid "Right. We can do this"
msgstr "對。我們做得到"

#. Id: 18073-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 5.0
#. -- Parent line: 4 (18071-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 18073-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "I can get the cages open. Follow my lead."
msgstr "我可以打開籠子。跟著我的指引。"

#. Id: 18074-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 5.0
#. -- Parent line: 4 (18071-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 18074-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Plan? I'm waiting to be rescued"
msgstr "計劃？我等著被救出來"

#. Id: 18093-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 6.0
#. -- Parent line: 5 (18074-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 18093-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Well, I hope your rescuers don't let you down..."
msgstr "好吧，我希望你的救援人員不要讓你失望......"

#. Id: 18075-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 5.0
#. -- Parent line: 4 (18071-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 18075-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Plan? No plan. We'll just wing it!"
msgstr "計劃？沒有計劃。我們只是躲開它！"

#. Id: 18092-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 7.0
#. -- Parent line: 6 (18091-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 18092-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "I've got nothing to lose. Let's do it."
msgstr "我沒有什麼可失去的。我們開始做吧。"

#. Id: 18060-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 1.0
#. -- Parent line: 0 (18052-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 18060-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Cheer up, at least you've got a roof over your head, eh?"
msgstr "振作起來，至少你頭上有一個屋頂，呃？"

#. Id: 18061-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 1.0
#. -- Parent line: 0 (18052-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 18061-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "I'm gonna break out of here. Are you with me?"
msgstr "我要離開這裡了。你跟我在一起嗎？"

#. Id: 18069-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 1.0
#. -- Parent line: 0 (18055-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 18069-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "You. You want to break out with me?"
msgstr "您。你想和我一起出去玩嗎？"

#. Id: 18070-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 2.0
#. -- Parent line: 1 (18069-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 18070-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "... You're busting out? I'll come with you... I serve no master, no slaver... no-one but me."
msgstr "你正在淘汰？我會和你一起去......我沒有主人，沒有奴隸......除了我，沒有人。"

#. Id: 18089-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 3.0
#. -- Parent line: 2 (18070-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 18089-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Good. I'll work the locks. Follow my lead"
msgstr "好。我會工作鎖。跟著我的指引"

#. Id: 19860-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 3.0
#. -- Parent line: 2 (18070-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 19860-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Sit tight, I'll handle the locks"
msgstr "坐下，我會處理鎖"

#. Id: 19861-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 3.0
#. -- Parent line: 2 (18070-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 19861-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Just leave it to me."
msgstr "請留給我。"

#. Id: 20076-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 4.0
#. -- Parent line: 3 (19861-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#. Id: 98484-__March 18.mod
#. -- Index: 4.0
#. -- Parent line: 3 (98483-__March 18.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: cannibal hunter talk to
#: 20076-Dialogue.mod:0 98484-__March?18.mod:0
msgid "... Right."
msgstr "... 對。"

#. Id: 18094-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 1.0
#. -- Parent line: 0 (18055-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 18094-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Still sane, neighbour?"
msgstr "還是理智，鄰居？"

#. Id: 18096-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 2.0
#. -- Parent line: 1 (18094-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 18096-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Still sane... They can take away my freedom but they won't take away my sanity... The Hive already did that once."
msgstr "仍然理智......他們可以剝奪我的自由，但他們不會帶走我的理智......蜂巢已經做過一次了。"

#. Id: 19856-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 3.0
#. -- Parent line: 2 (18096-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 19856-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Good. Then let's bust out of here, you and me."
msgstr "好。然後讓我們來到這裡，你和我。"

#. Id: 19859-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 4.0
#. -- Parent line: 3 (19856-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 19859-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Bust out?... Hell, count me in. I serve no master, no slaver, no-one."
msgstr "匆匆忙忙？...好吧，算我一點。我沒有主人，沒有奴隸，沒有人。"

#. Id: 19857-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 3.0
#. -- Parent line: 2 (18096-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 19857-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "So, you just gonna sit there, or are you gonna reclaim your freedom?"
msgstr "所以，你只是坐在那裡，或者你會收回你的自由？"

#. Id: 20075-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 4.0
#. -- Parent line: 3 (19857-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 20075-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Guess I've just been waiting for the right time... or.. maybe not. Those masters... I've never seen such cruelty before. I just can't summon the courage to rise up..."
msgstr "猜猜我一直在等待合適的時間......或者......也許不是。那些大師......我以前從未見過如此殘忍。我無法鼓起勇氣站起來......"

#. Id: 20077-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 5.0
#. -- Parent line: 4 (20075-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 20077-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Just leave it to me. I'll get you out."
msgstr "請留給我。我會幫你的"

#. Id: 20078-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 6.0
#. -- Parent line: 5 (20077-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 20078-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "You're busting out?... Okay... okay, count me in..."
msgstr "你要淘汰了？...好的......好吧，算我..."

#. Id: 20079-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 5.0
#. -- Parent line: 4 (20075-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 20079-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Screw them, I'm gonna make a run for it. Are you in?"
msgstr "搞砸它們，我要為它做好準備。你在嗎？"

#. Id: 20080-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 5.0
#. -- Parent line: 4 (20075-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 20080-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "So you'd rather live as their slave? Coward talk."
msgstr "所以你寧願像奴隸一樣生活？考沃德說。"

#. Id: 20081-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 6.0
#. -- Parent line: 5 (20080-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Me (0)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 20081-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "I serve no-one! No master! As soon as I get the chance, I WILL win my freedom..."
msgstr "我沒服務！沒有高手！一旦我有機會，我就會贏得自由..."

#. Id: 19862-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 3.0
#. -- Parent line: 2 (18096-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 19862-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "Then let's not let it happen again. Let's bust out."
msgstr "那麼我們不要再讓它發生了。讓我們破產吧。"

#. Id: 19863-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 3.0
#. -- Parent line: 2 (18096-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 19863-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "That's the spirit. Hang in there."
msgstr "就是那種精神。在那裡掛。"

#. Id: 18095-Dialogue.mod
#. -- Index: 1.0
#. -- Parent line: 0 (18055-Dialogue.mod)
#. -- Speaker: Target (1)
#. -- Group title: Enslaved hiver ronin
#: 18095-Dialogue.mod:0
msgid "At least you've got no hair to shave off, eh?"
msgstr "至少你沒有剃掉頭髮了，是嗎？"
